      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Predicted normalized index of hemolysis within factor of 2 of experimental mean across all operating points; systematic bias documented.",
      "rationale": "CFD predictions fall within a factor of 1.7 of experimental means at all five operating points. A consistent over-prediction bias of approximately 18% is noted and attributed to power-law hemolysis model constants. Achieved level 2 meets required level 2."
