      "acceptanceCriteria": "Turbulence model selection justified by comparison of k-ω SST and RSM predictions against experimental velocity profiles.",
      "rationale": "k-ω SST and Reynolds stress model predictions compared against PIV velocity data in the pump volute. k-ω SST shows lower RMS error on NIH-relevant shear stress distributions and is adopted. Model form uncertainty contribution estimated at 12% of NIH prediction via Monte Carlo sampling of model constants. Achieved level 2 meets required level 2."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
