      "rationale": "Monte Carlo analysis with 500 samples propagates uncertainty in Giersiepen-Wurzinger constants (C, α, β) and dynamic viscosity. The 95th-percentile NIH remains below the clinical threshold of 0.1 mg/dL per 100 L at all operating points. Achieved level 2 meets required level 2."
    },
